On the other cylinder, there's a blue cube (block #3) atop a yellow/orange rectangular block (block #9).  The top layer consists of a blue cube (block #3) on top of the other yellow/orange rectangular block (block #9) and an additional arch shape block (block #2) in between the two cylinders. Finally, a light yellowish-orange block (block #9) in the shape of a rectangle in the horizontal position sits next to these blocks.
